  "plot": [
    {
      "plot_summary": "The Fourth Doctor and Romana I arrive in Cornwall to locate the third segment of the Key to Time. They encounter stone circles and a Druidic cult. Vivien Fay is revealed to be the criminal Cessair of Diplos, who uses stones called Ogri to her advantage. The Doctor reveals her identity using justice machines, the Megara, which sentence her to be imprisoned as a stone. The Doctor retrieves the third segment of the Key, the Great Seal of Diplos."
    }
